metadata.name: PEPE Invasion
metadata.description:
To mark the rise in the PEPE Community and a moment in Web3 History,  I am releasing my first ever Crazy Hank Open Edition.

This piece of art stands as a testament to the PEPE movement and shows Hank meeting his Master ‘PEPE’.

Your opportunity to collect your first ever Crazy Hank artwork.

2000 x 2000 MP4 Video Animation with SFX

$PEPE
#PEPEARMY
#PEPE
